パッケージ ow.directory

インタフェースの概要
MultiValueDirectory<K,V> A directory that maps keys to values.
SingleValueDirectory<K,V> A directory that maps keys to values.
 

クラスの概要
DirectoryConfiguration  
DirectoryFactory  
DirectoryProvider The interface which a directory provider for various backend databases implements.
MultiValueAdapterForSingleValueDirectory<K,V> An adapter which converts a SingleValueDirectory to a MultiValueDirectory.
 

列挙型の概要
DirectoryConfiguration.HeapOverflowAction  
 

例外の概要
OutOfHeapException SingleValueDirectory#put and MultiValueDirectory#put throw this Exception when DirectoryConfiguration#getHeapOverflowAction() returns THROW_AN_OUT_OF_HEAP_EXCEPTION.
